  "2026-06-02T23:04:12.057Z",codex-continue-sdk-cli,"Sub-agent architecture lane: recommended a dedicated default-inert first-party lifecycle hook package instead of attaching a no-op hook to an unrelated workflow package. Reason: hooks activate globally on every matching lifecycle event, so the exemplar should be isolated, side-effect-free, and explicit; assertRegisteredHook should validate ExtensionActivationResult.hooks."
